{"tid":1758721,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"理大再出聲明: 警方無需再採取類似的行動，並立刻解封校園","createTime":"2019-11-27T08:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T09:37:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d37666ac3c993efdbb7ec4d5de7c9faef3e5f06d","tid":1758721,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:41:23.000Z","msg":"2019.11.27<br />\n香港理工大學聲明 (下午4時)<br />\n香港理工大學今天下午向政府提出以下三個要求:<br />\n<br />\n鑑於校方在這兩天已進行了全面尋找留守人士的工作，校方建議警方無需再採取類似的行動，並立刻解封校園。<br />\n要求相關的政府部門盡快處理校園内所有危險品，包括汽油彈和攻擊性武器等。<br />\n執行任何行動時，要以和平和人道方式，保障所有人士的人身安全。<br />\n香港理工大學<br />\n<br />\n主席 林大輝博士<br />\n校長 滕錦光教授<br />\n常務及學務副校長 陳正豪教授<br />\n行政副校長 盧麗華博士<br />\n副校長（校園發展及設施管理）唐仕恒先生<br />\n副校長（科研發展）衞炳江教授<br />\n副校長（學生事務）楊立偉教授<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.polyu.edu.hk/web/tc/media/media_releases/index_id_6718.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2Fweb%2Ftc%2Fmedia%2Fmedia_releases%2Findex_id_6718.html&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mREYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=a038ed23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.polyu.edu.hk/web/tc/media/media_releases/index_id_6718.html</a>"},{"pid":"42d34eaada2fed26730fcea854255a2181b9f7a0","tid":1758721,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:43:26.000Z","msg":"屌極都唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db369930dd2c3efde27c3cfc4d92c48a65656ab8","tid":1758721,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vq2VS6P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVq2VS6P.jpg&h=df2259db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKP5vTv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKP5vTv.jpg&h=24d6f0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動po